column5:
15 pages; v2: added explicit calculation of higher-spin toy-model;
  v3: minor changes to provide more context, references added, version accepted
  for publication in JHEP

Keywords: Suszko's thesis; truth value; logical consequence; mixed
  consequence; compositionality; truth-functionality; many-valued logic;
  algebraic logic; substructural logics; regular connectives

Added published data (journal, pages, etc.); correction of a typo;
  updated details of one reference; a slight change to the margins (to allow
  the last page, with the addresses, to be merged with the penultimate page)
